'''Slavelord Boulevard''' was the name of a street found in the capital city of [[Kessendra]] on the planet, [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]]. Its original designation is unknown, but the name was changed to Slavelord Boulevard at some point during the reign of [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor Palpatine]]. The street intersects with [[Spice Mines Avenue]]. [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] once got lost on Slavelord Boulevard after returning from a spy mission at the [[Kessendra Stadium]].

